version_description: The chords were sounded out by ear with my own singing, so the key is slightly higher than the original song.
Simplified everything. Beginner friendly, and an easier way of transitioning the chords. Replaced the "F" chord to "Fmaj7" so no Barre chords. Played by ear.
Tab is set up to be played as a single guitar (electric or acoustic would both work). I've included two strum patterns which will work well for this song.
Using a capo make easier to play simple chords for the song.
Sounds better if it's played muted on the verses, and bar chords on the chorus.
Includes additional tablature based on their "zankyou reference concert 2012" tour.
